PrecisAmendments to the MEDICAL DEVICES REGULATIONS (Part V) that are designed to ensure that all AIDS test kits continue to be subject to pre-market review, irrespective of the media in which the AIDS indicative marker is found, and to ensure consistency in the wording of regulatory provisions related to HIV test kits.
